# user-stories.md

1. As a student, I want to search for a course by its code so that I can quickly find it.

2. As a student, I want to view all available courses so that I can choose courses for registration.

3. As a student, I want to register for a course so that I can enroll in the semester.

4. As a student, I want to view my registered courses so that I can track my schedule.

5. As a student, I want to check prerequisites so that I know whether I am eligible for a course.

6. As a student, I want to see available seats so that I can know if registration is possible.

7. As a student, I want the system to detect schedule conflicts so that I do not register for overlapping courses.

8. As a student, I want to identify full courses so that I can choose alternatives.

9. As an instructor, I want to view enrolled students so that I can manage my course.

10. As a student, I want to create a semester plan so that I can organize my academic progress.
